  "title": "Retail Shop Assistant (POS System)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Basic $2,000 - $2,600 + AWS + VB</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working Location: Bishan (Walking distance from MRT)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working Days: Tuesday - Saturday (5 days)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Working Hours: 9.00am - 6.30pm</strong><br /></p><p><br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide friendly and helpful customer service</p></li><li><p><strong>Assist customers with product enquiries and purchase decisions</strong></p></li><li><p>Process cash and card payments accurately</p></li><li><p><strong>Handle customer enquiries and orders</strong> via email and WhatsApp</p></li><li><p><strong>Assist with order packing and preparation</strong></p></li><li><p>Receive, organise, and restock inventory</p></li><li><p>Keep the shop clean, tidy, and well organised</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Other ad hoc duties as assigned</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prior experience in Retail or customer service</p></li><li><p><strong>Experience with POS systems will be an advantage</strong></p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li><p>Work experiences and job responsibilities</p></li><li><p>Current and Expected salary</p></li><li><p>Reason for leaving</p></li><li><p>Date of availability</p></li><li><p>Education background</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br /></p><p></p><p>NG JYA YEE (R23119014)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
